			"name": "Spectral Duplicate",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>Hadkor creeates a mental duplicate of himself in an unoccupied space within 60 feet of Hadkor. While the duplicate exist, Hadkor is considered @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fBnFDH2MTzgFijKf]{Unconscious}, as he acts through his duplicate, which has the same statistics and knowledge of the original, and everything the duplicate experiences is known by the original. All the physical damage dealed by the duplicate are considered mental. If Hadkor or the duplicate is reduced to 0 hp, the duplicated cease to exist. Hadkor can have only one duplicate active at the time.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
				"publication": {
